                  </persName>
            , the officer, produced the property, which was deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I had been drinking in the house for three quarters of an hour; when I was coming away, these things were lying at the bottom of the box, and I kicked them before me.</p>
